description: Cedergrenska AB is a SE-based company operating in  industry. The company is headquartered in Stocksund, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2021-05-25. Cedergrenska AB is a Sweden-based education group that conducts education for children and students from preschool to post-secondary education. The Company’s model is based on conducting school activities within smaller geographical clusters, which promotes synergies between schools through collaborations and the use of group-wide assets, such as facilities and support functions. Cedergrenska runs, among others primary schools Taby Friskola and Fredsborgskolan, as well as some after upper secondary schools in Tibble Gymnasium Campus Taby, Marina Laroverket and Stockholms Idrottsgymnasium.
